1
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:05,200
Do you remember Lin Chuyi,

2
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:07,719
your old classmate

3
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,200
with whom you had a deep bond?

4
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,200
Lin Chuyi?

5
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,480
Who is she?

6
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,680
I don't remember.

7
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,959
Get some rest.

8
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,079
I'll go find the doctor.

9
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:37,920
Any news on Jiang Xun?

10
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,079
She's back in Rongzhou.

11
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,480
The Jiang family is currently

12
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,799
in Rongzhou.

13
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,519
Should we keep an eye on her?

14
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,439
By the way,

15
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,959
Ke Yu'ang went to see her.

16
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,799
If someone does something wrong,

17
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,920
they'll naturally try to make amends.

18
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,400
If he's smart,

19
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:11,000
he'll get the cryptographic key from Jiang Xun.

20
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:13,039
If not,

21
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,479
someone will deal with him.

22
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,080
He deserves it.

23
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,599
[Shen Shutu has lost his memory,]

24
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,439
[and the state security has lost contact with him.]

25
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,599
[The last time I saw him showing off at the bar,]

26
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:27,680
[he seemed to know about the cryptographic key.]

27
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:30,479
[He mistook me for Jiang Xun.]

28
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,400
Take this chance to restore his memory.

29
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,000
[to explore the intelligence of Rongzhou.]

30
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:38,240
[It would be best to find out the cryptographic key from him.]

31
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:41,080
Get your men on their toes.

32
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:42,560
From now on,

33
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:45,319
you must call me Miss Jiang.

34
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,479
Yes, Miss Jiang.

35
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,560
[Shen Shutu,]

36
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,199
[if you want to act,]

37
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,599
[I'll play along.]

38
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,199
[If you've really lost your memory,]

39
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:55,400
[that's just what I want.]

40
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,159
Hello?

41
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,039
[Ms Jiang,]

42
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:11,439
[a customer named Wu left a manuscript.]

43
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,400
[He specifically requested you to restore it.]

44
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,120
Okay, send it to me.

45
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,319
Wu Shixuan?

46
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,599
Sounds familiar.

47
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,439
Wu Shixuan.

48
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,159
In my dream,

49
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,719
he was the leader of Great-Grandparents.

50
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,520
Is this Mr. Wu

51
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,319
his descendant?

52
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,639
I'm so tired.

53
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,000
Let's go have dinner later.

54
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,399
What's for dinner?

55
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,720
We'll see.

56
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,399
How could this happen?

57
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,439
I should have dragged you back to Rongzhou.

58
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,639
It's all my fault.

59
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,759
Are you a nurse?

60
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,519
You...

61
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,839
Have we

62
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,920
met before?

63
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:39,000
Shen Shutu,

64
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,079
now is not the time to play the amnesia card.

65
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,839
I'm not.

66
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,839
You're not a nurse here.

67
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,439
Who are you?

68
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,199
You...

69
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,839
Don't you remember me?

70
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:59,040
Should I?

71
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:03,879
My name is Jiang Xun.

72
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,759
I'm from Rongzhou.

73
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:08,120
My great-grandfather

74
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,680
is Jiang Chihui,

75
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:11,959
My great-grandmother

76
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,240
was Song Jin'an.

77
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,000
We're in a relationship.

78
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,680
I came to see you today.

79
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,560
Wait.

80
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:19,759
Why should I know

81
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,160
who your ancestors are?

82
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,079
What do your great-grandparents

83
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:24,120
have to do with me?

84
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,360
And

85
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,839
you said

86
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,800
your name is Jiang Xun, too.

87
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,600
What does it mean?

88
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,720
You said

89
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:33,959
too?

90
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,079
Who else?

91
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,560
You gave me this dragon pendant.

92
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,800
You said you wore it since childhood,

93
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,839
and it's a part of you.

94
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:57,199
We've been through so much together.

95
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,000
Don't you remember anything?

96
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,680
What's going on?

97
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,160
Why?

98
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,920
Why would you...

99
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,120
Shen Shutu,

100
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,720
no matter if you remember me,

101
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,399
I'll come back for you.

102
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,399
Xunxun, you finally came to see me.

103
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,079
Shutu,

104
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,519
I've got your discharge papers.

105
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,800
Move in with me tomorrow.

106
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,279
Okay.

107
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,480
Eat.

108
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,000
Hu.

109
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:07,879
Jiang Xun.

110
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:10,079
Do you know how dangerous it was just now?

111
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,600
If we hadn't been protecting you...

112
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,560
Shen Shutu is in trouble.

113
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,879
It's all my fault.

114
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,279
I was too impulsive.

115
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,040
Don't worry.

116
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,319
We have a plan.

117
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,800
Go back to Rongzhou right now.

118
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,679
I'm sorry.

119
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,000
I didn't mean to ignore you.

120
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,120
I have my plan.

121
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,240
Come here to find me tomorrow morning.

122
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,720
Shen Shutu.

123
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,399
Shen Shutu.

124
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:31,840
Xunxun.

125
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,919
Please get me a towel.

126
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,039
I forgot to take it.

127
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,799
Who are you?

128
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,279
How...

129
00:10:00,279 --> 00:10:02,279
How come it's you again?

130
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,720
How did you find this place?

131
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,480
Didn't you ask me to come?

132
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,919
When did I ask you to come?

133
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,039
Miss nurse,

134
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:14,000
you wouldn't know my family is rich,

135
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:16,120
so you take advantage of my injury

136
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,240
to get close to me, would you?

137
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,320
What are you doing?

138
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,440
Why do you hit me?

139
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,120
I'm beating you for your poor memory.

140
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,480
Whether your memory loss is real or not,

141
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:28,919
I shouldn't have come to you today.

142
00:10:30,919 --> 00:10:31,720
Wait a minute.

143
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,639
You said

144
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,320
you're Jiang Xun.

145
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:41,279
Then what about my fiancée?

146
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,399
Who is she?

147
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,799
You'll know who she is later.

148
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,240
Shen Shutu,

149
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,840
I shouldn't have contacted you.

150
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:52,120
I shouldn't have sent you messages.

151
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,639
From now on,

152
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,320
we are strangers.

153
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:41,600
[In the drama, I risked my reputation to secretly infiltrate]

154
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:43,960
[just to fulfill the sacred mission entrusted to me by the Party.]

155
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,000
[In history,]

156
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,200
[countless predecessors on the covert front]

157
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,159
[infiltrated the enemy's ranks]

158
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,720
[to protect the country's peace with their nameless bodies.]

159
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,960
They made immortal contributions

160
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,120
to the founding of New China and its people's liberation.

161
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:56,919
From the years of war to the prosperous present,

162
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:59,159
national security has never been far from us.

163
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:02,200
On the new journey of building a strong country and national rejuvenation,

164
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,840
everyone is a guardian of national security.
